// info strings
Chameleon feature

    When chameleon feature is enabled, users can open eBrain app with wrong passwords but private notes and tasks will be hidden.


Repeatable


    if task is repeatable, that mean it won\'t be destroyed or deleted when it\'s complete.


Privacy


    if "task/note" is private and chameleon feature was enabled, this "task/note" will be hidden from unauthorized users.

